DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260715
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260716
SUMMARY:First Rikers remediation action plan due
DESCRIPTION:Nicholas Deml\, appointed the court's Nunez remediation manag
 er on Feb. 23\, 2026\, is scheduled to submit his first remediation acti
 on plan in mid-July. The court declined to impose a receivership in May 
 2025 and installed a remediation manager instead. Date approximate withi
 n mid-July.\n\nhttps://www.nyc.gov/site/doc/media/nunez-reports.page
URL:https://www.nyc.gov/site/doc/media/nunez-reports.page
CATEGORIES:justice
