DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260901
SUMMARY:One year until Rikers must close
DESCRIPTION:Administrative Code section 4-215\, from Local Law 16 of 2021
 \, requires that by Aug. 31\, 2027 all of Rikers Island be transferred o
 ut of the Correction Department's control and no longer used to house pe
 ople. This marks exactly one year out.
