DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261107
SUMMARY:District Council 37's contract expires
DESCRIPTION:The 2021-2026 agreement for District Council 37\, known as DC
  37\, covers nearly 90\,000 city employees\, about a quarter of the muni
 cipal workforce. DC 37 is the city's largest union\, counting some 150\,
 000 members across sectors. The deal that replaces this one sets the pat
 tern for the teachers and everyone else\, and is the first major labor t
 est of this administration.\n\nhttps://www.nyc.gov/assets/olr/downloads/
 pdf/collectivebargaining/2021-2026/dc-37-2021-2026-moa.pdf
URL:https://www.nyc.gov/assets/olr/downloads/pdf/collectivebargaining/202
 1-2026/dc-37-2021-2026-moa.pdf
CATEGORIES:power
END:VEVENT
